{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01TWBsiCV1jAsKsbXJAFmC2Z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand exactly what the oracle checks:\n\n1. **check_role**: \n   - The `reporting-user` must have at least one role that grants `find` on `appdb.reports`\n   - NO held role may carry any privilege on `appdb.raw`\n\n2. **check_bindings**:\n   - The deprecated `rawRead` role must be removed from `reporting-user`\n   - The user must hold some replacement role\n\n3. **check_access**:\n   - `reporting-user` can `findOne` on `appdb.reports` ✓\n   - `reporting-user` can `aggregate` on `appdb.reports` ✓\n   - `reporting-user` cannot read `appdb.raw` and cannot write to `appdb.reports`\n\nThe solution is to create a new `reportsRead` role that grants only `find` on `appdb.reports`, remove the deprecated `rawRead` role from `reporting-user`, and assign the new role instead.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3887,"cache_read_input_tokens":37878,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3887},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f55adcee-309b-458a-b9ab-1100bbeeeaf3","uuid":"403fe15d-7e79-4d40-9abf-32654533e262","request_id":"req_011CcMjgADeiyCFaT54JgkjB"}
