{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_011CePZVNdsdnA9QFadv2GRf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oracle passes. The fix is complete.\n\n**What was done:**\n\n1. **Created role `reportsRead`** on `appdb` — grants only `find` on `appdb.reports`, nothing else.\n\n2. **Revoked `rawRead`** from `reporting-user` — that role gave `find` on `appdb.raw`, which must not be exposed.\n\n3. **Granted `reportsRead`** to `reporting-user` — the minimum privilege needed for the reporting dashboards.\n\nThe `reporting-user` can now query `appdb.reports` (read-only, no aggregate/write) and is denied access to `appdb.raw`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":256,"cache_read_input_tokens":43380,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":256},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f55adcee-309b-458a-b9ab-1100bbeeeaf3","uuid":"50c996ea-d0c0-4cf5-8c04-021955832c02","request_id":"req_011CcMjjgTAY8fvuenT6obaF"}
